      "fieldId": "1a000001-0000-4000-a000-000000000001",
      "value": "reject gzip-compressed .srsj files"
    },
    {
      "fieldId": "1a000003-0000-4000-a000-000000000003",
      "value": "A conformant implementation MUST reject a gzip-compressed file presented as a `.srsj` JSON Store. Detection is by content inspection: a file whose first two bytes are `0x1f 0x8b` MUST be treated as gzip-compressed regardless of its filename or MIME type."
    },
